name: ExtensionEvidenceReport_Section
title: Cross-version Extension `R5.EvidenceReport.section` for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents the FHIR R5 element `EvidenceReport.section` for use in FHIR R4.
purpose:
This extension is part of the cross-version definitions generated to enable use of the
element `EvidenceReport.section` as defined in FHIR R5
in FHIR R4.

The source element is defined as:
`EvidenceReport.section` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Across FHIR versions, the element set has been mapped as:
*  R5: `EvidenceReport.section` 0..* `BackboneElement`

Following are the generation technical comments:
Element `EvidenceReport.section` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `EvidenceReport` is not mapped.
